         libjson-perl,
         multipath-tools
Description: Proxmox VE storage plugin for Hitachi block storage
 Storage plugin for Proxmox VE that integrates with Hitachi FC-based
 block storage systems (VSP G series and VSP One Block).
 Provides 1 LUN per virtual disk with array-offloaded storage services
 including snapshots, clones, and online resize.
